            <h3 class="heading-medium">Before you start</h3>
          
            <p>To get your first provisional driving licence online for a car, motorcycle or moped you must:</p>
            
            <ul class="list-bullet">
              <li>be a resident of Great Britain &ndash; there’s a different service in <a href="http://www.nidirect.gov.uk/applying-for-a-provisional-driving-licence" rel="external">Northern Ireland</a></li>
              <li>meet the minimum age requirement</li>
              <li>meet the <a href="/driving-eyesight-rules">minimum eyesight requirement</a></li>
              <li>not be prevented from driving for any reason</li>
              <li>pay &pound;50 by MasterCard, Visa, Electron, Maestro or Delta debit or credit card</li>
              <li>have a valid <abbr title="United Kngdom">UK</abbr> passport or <a href="/driving-licence-application-identity-documents">other form of identity</a></li>
              <li>have your National Insurance number if known</li>
              <li>provide addresses where you’ve lived for the last 3 years</li>
            </ul>
          
          </div>
        
        </div>
      
        <div class="tabs-panel" id="need-to-know">
          
          <div class="tabs-panel-inner text">
            
            <h3 class="heading-medium">Need to know</h3>
        
            <ul class="list-bullet">
              <li>Proof of identification required</li>
              <li>3 years of address details required</li>
              <li>Debit or credit card required</li>
            </ul>
          
          </div>
          
        </div>
        
        <div class="tabs-panel" id="ways-to-apply">
        
          <div class="tabs-panel-inner text">
            
            <h3 class="heading-medium">Ways to apply</h3>
          
            <p>You can apply by post by completing a D1 application form, which you can get from the <a href="#"><abbr title="Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency">DVLA</abbr> form ordering service</a> or from a Post Office.</p>
            
            <p>You’ll also need to include:</p>
            
            <ul class="list-bullet">
              <li>original documentation confirming your identity</li>
              <li>a colour <a href="/photos-for-passports">passport-style photograph</a></li>
              <li>the fee of &pound;50 by cheque or postal order payable to <abbr title="Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency">DVLA</abbr> (do not send cash)</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>Send your completed application and payment to <abbr title="Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency">DVLA</abbr>, Swansea, SA99 1AD.</p>
            
            <p>If you’re including non&ndash;<abbr title="United Kingdom">UK</abbr> identity documents send your application and payment to <abbr title="Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency">DVLA</abbr>, Swansea, SA99 1AF.</p>
          
          </div>
        
